snippet.title: Annalynn - Version 1.3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Version 1.3 of Annalynn has finally arrived, and it's a big one! Play through all the levels out of order in random mode with extra goodies like power ups and bonus stages!

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1508460/Annalynn/
itch.io page: https://cruise-elroy.itch.io/annalynn

Trailer music by Isaac Riley: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCClEHLv8sL3cfVodS5BKDSA/featured
Promo art by SparkBag: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVc8X2lijepSdo4or_FYjXw
